001 Paul,
    a slave of anointed Yeshua,
    a called sent one,
    having been marked,
    for the good announcement of God,
002     which He on-announced before,
            by His before-sayers,
            in set apart writings,
003     concerning His Son,
            the one generated from seed of David,
                according to flesh,
004         having been marked Son of God,
                in ability,
                according to a spirit of set apartness,
                by the standing up of the dead,
            Yeshua anointed,
            our master.
